{
  "texts": [
    "In natural Building Customized Chatbots for Document Summarization and Question Answering using Large Language Models using a Framework with OpenAI, Lang chain, and Streamlit ISSN: 2582-418X 78 language processing (NLP), word embeddings are frequently employed to depict words as vectors within a high-dimensional space.",
    "This representation arranges words with akin meanings closer together in the vector space.",
    "These embeddings can be generated through diverse techniques, including Word2Vec, GloVe, or deep learning models like transformers.In this paper, we utilized the OpenAI embeddings class from the LangChain embeddings.OpenAI module.",
    "It is a part of the LangChain package and provides embeddings based on OpenAI's language models for text data.",
    "A vector store, also known as a knowledge base, is a repository where embeddings or vectors representing data are stored."
  ]
}